Mortality associated with coronavirus in HCT recipients was inconclusive. While some studies [

 9

] reported no associations, other studies [

 10

] reported similar mortality rates in HCT recipients to those observed with other viruses such as RSV, influenza virus, and PIV.

Paediatric patients with cancer and acute respiratory infection [

 14

] and/or fever.

